<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<title>HaloMed | Frequently Asked Questions</title>
<link rel="stylesheet" href="css/faq.css">
<link rel="shortcut icon" href="images/halomed1.png">
</head>
<body>
<%@ include file="header.jsp" %>
<br>
<div class="container">
        <h1>Frequently Asked Questions</h1>

        <!-- HALOMED ACCOUNT & REGISTRATION Section -->
        <div class="faq-section">
            <h2 class="section-title">ACCOUNT & REGISTRATION</h2>
            <div class="faq-items">
                <div class="faq-item">
                    <div class="question-title">1. What is HaloMed user registration?</div>
                    <div class="answer">
                        Registering with HaloMed gives you access to our complete range of digital health-care services 
                        including doctor appointments, tele-medicine, and health records management.
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="faq-item">
                    <div class="question-title">2.  How do I create a HaloMed account?</div>
                    <div class="answer">
                    	Three simple ways to register: <br>
                    	<ol>
                    		<li>Website: Visit <span class="highlight">www.halomed.lk</span> and click Sign Up </li>
                        	<li>Mobile App: Download from App Store/Google Play </li>
                        	<li>Hotline: Call 011 7 123 123 </li>
                    	</ol>
                    	You'll need your mobile number, email, and NIC/Passport details.
                	</div>
                </div>

                <div class="faq-item">
                    <div class="question-title">3. Is there a registration fee?</div>
                    <div class="answer">
                        Account registration is completely free. Charges only apply when you book services like doctor 
                        appointments or subscribe to health packages.
                    </div>
                </div>
                
        	</div>
		</div>
        
		<!-- HALOMED BOOKING & APPOINTMENTS Section -->
        <div class="faq-section">
            <h2 class="section-title">BOOKING & APPOINTMENTS</h2>
            <div class="faq-items">
                <div class="faq-item">
                    <div class="question-title">1. How do I book a doctor appointment?</div>
                    <div class="answer">
                        <ol>
	                        <li>Login to your HaloMed account </li>
							<li>Search for doctor/hospital </li>
							<li>Select date & time slot </li>
							<li>Confirm payment </li>
							<li>Receive SMS/email confirmation </li>
						</ol>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="faq-item">
                    <div class="question-title">2.  Can I book for family members?</div>
                    <div class="answer">
                    	Yes! You can book appointments for family members by adding them as dependents in your profile.
                </div>
                </div>

                <div class="faq-item">
                    <div class="question-title">3. What if I need to cancel/reschedule?</div>
                    <div class="answer">
                        Through your HaloMed account: <br>
                        <ul>
                        	<li>Cancellations: Up to 24 hours before for full refund </li>
							<li>Rescheduling: Available if done 12 hours prior </li>
							<li>No-show: Service fee may be forfeited </li>
                        </ul>	
                    </div>
                </div>

       		</div>
		</div>

		<!-- HALOMED PAYMENTS & REFUNDS Section -->
        <div class="faq-section">
            <h2 class="section-title">PAYMENTS & REFUNDS</h2>
            <div class="faq-items">
                <div class="faq-item">
                    <div class="question-title">1. What payment methods are accepted?</div>
                    <div class="answer">
                        <ul>
                        	<li>Credit/Debit Cards (Visa, Mastercard) </li>
							<li>Mobile Wallets (eZ Cash, mCash) </li>
							<li>Bank Transfers </li>
							<li>Insurance (selected providers) </li>
						</ul>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="faq-item">
                    <div class="question-title">2. When will I get my refund?</div>
                    <div class="answer">
                    	Refunds are processed within 3-5 working days. The time-frame depends on your payment method: <br>
						<ul>
							<li>Cards: 3-5 business days </li>
							<li>Bank Transfers: 2-3 business days </li>
							<li>Mobile Wallets: Instant to 24 hours </li>
						</ul>
                	</div>
                </div>

       		</div>
		</div>

		<!-- HALOMED TECHNICAL SUPPORT Section -->
        <div class="faq-section">
            <h2 class="section-title">TECHNICAL SUPPORT</h2>
            <div class="faq-items">
                <div class="faq-item">
                    <div class="question-title">1.  I didn't receive my booking confirmation</div>
                    <div class="answer">
                        <ul>
	                        <li>First check your spam/junk folder. If still missing: </li>
							<li>Verify your contact details in profile </li>
							<li>Check app notifications </li>
							<li>Contact support with your booking reference </li>
						</ul>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="faq-item">
                    <div class="question-title">2. The app isn't working properly</div>
                    <div class="answer">
                    	Try these troubleshooting steps:<br>
                    	<ul>
                    		<li>Update to latest app version </li>
							<li>Clear cache/data </li>
							<li>Restart your device </li>
							<li>Reinstall the app </li>
                    	</ul>
                    	If issues persist, contact our technical team.
                	</div>
                </div>

       		</div>
		</div>
		
		<!-- HALOMED SERVICES Section -->
        <div class="faq-section">
            <h2 class="section-title">SERVICES</h2>
            <div class="faq-items">
                <div class="faq-item">
                    <div class="question-title">1. What services does HaloMed offer?</div>
                    <div class="answer">
                        <ul>
                        	<li>Telemedicine: Video/audio consultations</li>
							<li>Medicine Delivery: Islandwide service</li>
							<li>Lab Services: Home collection and online reports</li>
							<li>Corporate Health: Employee wellness programs</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="faq-item">
                    <div class="question-title">2. Are online prescriptions valid?</div>
                    <div class="answer">
                    	Yes, prescriptions from HaloMed's registered doctors are valid at all licensed 
                    	pharmacies in Sri Lanka.
                	</div>
                </div>

       		</div>
		</div>

		<p>Still have questions?<br><br>
			Our customer care team is available 24/7<br>
			
			Hotline: 011 7 123 123<br>
			Email: support@halomed.lk<br><br>
			Live Chat available in mobile app</p>

        <script>
            // Toggle topic sections
            document.querySelectorAll('.section-title').forEach(section => {
                section.addEventListener('click', () => {
                    section.classList.toggle('active');
                });
            });

            // Toggle questions
            document.querySelectorAll('.question-title').forEach(question => {
                question.addEventListener('click', () => {
                    question.classList.toggle('active');
                });
            });
        </script>
    </div>
    <%@ include file="footer.jsp" %>
</body>
</html>